NOTE: INNSTALL A VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENT BY TYPING: "py -m venv venv" in terminal and then install the following libraries in the terminal itself
Make a python virtual environment on powershell and activate it:

cd path_to_folder (replace path_to_folder with the path to the repository)
py -m venv venv
venv/Scripts/activate.ps1 (or) venv/Scripts/activate (Basically activate the vitrual environment)

installed libraries:
pip install pyaudio opencv-contrib-python numpy pyinstaller google-generativeai gtts speechrecognition pygame playsound

requirements:
python 3.10.11

To run the code, run main.py
